		<!-- Sidebar With Content Section-->
		<div class="with-sidebar-wrapper"><section id="content-section-2" ><div class="section-container container"><div class="gdlr-stunning-text-ux gdlr-ux"><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-stunning-text-item type-center" ><h2 class="stunning-text-title">We hire the best candidates to implement tomorrow's technology, marketing strategies and sales solutions.</h2><div class="stunning-text-caption"><p>As a family, we strive to be &#8220;A Great Place to Work, and a Great Place to be a Customer&#8221; &#8212; because we know that as a family we can a make the difference!</p>
</div></div></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-content-item" ><p>Saxon provides opportunity, support, attractive compensation, and a collaborative work environment&#8230;where people really count! As you are visiting our web site, we hope that you will gain a good appreciation for the rewarding aspects of a career with our company.</p>
<p>Saxon&#8217;s partners rely on their core values: ETHICAL, COLLABORATIVE, and ACCOUNTABLE are guiding principles in each interaction and decision. The Saxon Career Advantage offers exciting rewards and fulfilling experiences, personally and professionally. We are committed to your career development and success here at Saxon.</p>
<p> </p>
</div><div class="clear"></div><div class="gdlr-stunning-text-ux gdlr-ux"><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-stunning-text-item type-normal with-padding with-border" ><h2 class="stunning-text-title">Equal Employment Opportunity:</h2><div class="stunning-text-caption"><p>Saxon Business Systems Inc. maintains a policy of nondiscrimination with all employees and applicants for employment. All aspects of employment with us will be governed on the basis of merit, competence and qualifications and will not be influenced in any manner by race, color, religion, sex, age, national origin, disability, or any other basis prohibited by statute.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="gdlr-item gdlr-content-item" ><h2>Benefits:</h2>
<p>Saxon Business Systems offers a comprehensive suite of benefits to promote health and financial security for you and your family.</p>
<p>Our Benefits at Saxon are designed to give you choice, flexibility, and to encourage you and your family to adapt a healthier lifestyle.</p>
<ul>
<li>Generous Medical, Dental &#038; Vision Plan</li>
<li>Flexible Spending Accounts for Healthcare and Dependent Care</li>
<li>401(k) Retirement Savings Plan with (matching)</li>
<li>Company Paid Life Insurance, Company Paid Long Term Disability &#038; Short Term Disability</li>
<li>Company Paid Vacation, Sick and Holidays</li>
<li>Company Paid Employee Assistance Plan – to assist with all areas of life</li>
<li>Legal Plan</li>
<li>Xerox Discounts</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Sales Performance Bonuses</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Monthly Employee Recognition</li>
<li>Knights Club Incentive Awards Trip</li>
<li>Monthly &#038; Quarterly Sales Incentive Promotions</li>
<li>Quarterly Bonus Opportunities</li>
<li>Global Leaders Program</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Training and Education</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Sales Training and Development Program</li>
<li>Service Product Training</li>
<li>E-Learning Classes</li>
<li>In-field Training</li>
<li>Full Product Knowledge (In-house and Manufacturer Provided)</li>
<li>Continual Technology Training</li>
<li>Xerox Learning Center</li>
</ul>
